# Captain Boat — Project Memory

## Architecture Decisions (ADR log)

| # | Decision | Rationale | Date |
|---|----------|-----------|------|
| 1 | Full Next.js (no Express) | Simplify infra, single deploy | 2025-05 |
| 2 | Supabase for DB + Auth + Storage | Managed PostgreSQL, no self-host | 2025-05 |
| 3 | Stripe as single payment gateway | Card, AliPay, Apple Pay, Google Pay | 2025-05 |
| 4 | QR codes pre-generated by supplier | No generation needed, just DB+assign | 2025-05 |
| 5 | Guest checkout only (no accounts) | Simplified UX, cookie-based recall | 2025-05 |
| 6 | BNESIM for eSIM provisioning | API-based, mock mode if no creds | 2025-05 |
| 7 | String-based email templates | Zero-dep, no React Email runtime | 2025-05 |
| 8 | Mailpit dev → Resend prod | Same sender interface, env switch | 2025-05 |
| 9 | Stripe Proxy pattern | Lazy init avoids build-time crash | 2025-05 |
| 10 | Python FastAPI for RAG chatbot | Separate service, LangChain+pgvector | 2025-05 |

